steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitapi005" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitapi005" display
When I add new column with Name "jitapicol005" Type "string" for Table name "jitapi005"
When I navigate to menu "API" with submenu "API endpoints"
Then I should see API screen display
When I select api name "jitapi005s" from list
When I edit API method "PUT" with endpoint "/api/jitapi005s/:id"
When I delete query table "2" row "1"
Then I should NOT see floating panel has Model - DefinitionValue Table "2" - row "1" - value "jitapi005s.jitapicol005","request.jitapi005s.jitapicol005"
When I click tab "Request params" in Params of floating panel
When I expand the row name "jitapi005s"
When I delete params row "2"
Then I should NOT see floating panel has Params - row "2" - value "jitapicol005","String".
When I click tab "Response params" in Params of floating panel
When I expand the row name "jitapi005s"
When I delete params row "5"

When I close the floating panel
When I edit API method "PUT" with endpoint "/api/jitapi005s/:id"
